title: Bad Gifts and Dead Pets - EP4
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


This episode the Babes talk dealing with bad gifts from the holidays, Sal deals with gift card anxiety to G Star and Chris gets gifted Fubu from an aunt, buying irregular clothes for discounts, Chris has a bad shirtless body, Casting director tells Chris he has leading man face and best friend body, Boxing in Kentucky, Failed pilots and how the Impractical Jokers got made, Chris meeting his baby momma, 1 drink wont change your life, Sal bought his first mattress in 2010, Sal bought a bar before a mattress, driving while tired, Sal order a pizza and only ate the toppings, Sal kills a blind cat by accident, a bug interrupts the show, we find photos of Sal from Highschool, Chris accidentally killed his own dog when he was a boy, Chris’s fart sounds like theme song of Whats Happening, Chris’ friend murders his family dog at a house party, RIP Larry they didn't put him down right.


Rate us on iTunes! Follow us on social media @HeyBabePod
